headline: Leerink Partners Lifts Edwards Lifesciences (EW) Price Target Amid Buybacks Focus
summary: Edwards Lifesciences Corporation (NYSE:EW) is one of the top stock picks in Ken Griffin’s portfolio. On August 20, analysts at Leerink Partners reiterated a ‘Market Perform’ rating and hiked the stock’s price target to $85 from $84. The price target hike comes as the stock outperforms the overall market, rallying by 11% year to date. […]
